      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.DR8JvF0xiwsXggxj]{Expertise Talent}</p>\n<p>Choose a skill you have selected with the skill expertise class feature. When you take 20 (see page 133) with this skill, you can roll your [[/r 2d(lookupRange(@classes.envoy.levels,6,13,8))k+lookupRange(@classes.envoy.levels,0,5,1,9,2,17,3,20,4)]]{expertise die} twice and take the better result.</p>\n<p>You can choose this talent up to three times, choosing a different skill selected with the skill expertise class feature each time.</p>\n<p><em>Change selected skill in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
